<br>
My wife, Yakuza, and myself were camping a spire outside of Paw in S.Karana.  Suddenly I see these two characters come alone.  Zxvovxz (a dark elven  enchanter) had chamed an elephant and attacked the spawn Yak and I were at.  They, then, proceeded to stand next to me and point blank tell us that they were &quot;taking over&quot; that spawn.  I informed him I was there first, but they gave no time for compomise and told me they were there first (after Yak and I have been there for at least 25 minutes prior to this insident).<br>
<br>
After a while they take off after the attempted to take another gnoll from Yak and myself, but we outdamaged it and got the XP.  But a moment later I see those two miscreants back by Yak and me again.  Two others show up... Zelon and Gnomie (very nice folks, I might add), who complained that Zxvovxz and Lanthily just got done KSing their group, too!  Here went my next plan of action...<br>
<br>
I petitioned!<br>
<br>
About 20 minutes after I petitioned, a guide contacts me, by the name of Tayar or Tayal (I beleive).  The guide informs me that Zxvovxz has been trouble before, even having been suspended for the same offence....<br>
<br>
I was asked to keep an eye out for Zxvovxz and Lanthily and use /report next time they do this again.  I encourage the rest of you to do the same.  I really don;t like it when my, Yakuza's, or anyone else's EQ experience is ruined by such riff-raff.  Zxvovxz and Lanthily are nothing but daft, rude, and selfish!<br>
<br>
Thank you all for your support and cooperation in this matter.  It is greatly appreciated. <p>Mildikin Quartzworth<BR>
